# Create GitHub Project for TypeScript Projects

## When to Create

Only if repository has no linked GitHub Project.

## Check for Existing Project

```bash
# List projects for user
gh project list --owner ${GITHUB_OWNER}

# Check if project exists
gh project list --owner ${GITHUB_OWNER} | grep -i "${PROJECT_DISPLAY_NAME}"
```

## Create New Project

```bash
# Copy from template project
gh api graphql -f query='
  mutation {
    copyProjectV2(input: {
      projectId: "${PROJECT_TEMPLATE_ID}"
      ownerId: "${GITHUB_OWNER}"
      title: "${PROJECT_DISPLAY_NAME} Development"
    }) {
      projectV2 {
        id
        number
      }
    }
  }
'

# Returns: PROJECT_NUMBER
```

## Template Includes

