## Add Issues to Project

```bash
# Manually add issue to project
gh project item-add 1 --owner ${GITHUB_OWNER} --url "https://github.com/${GITHUB_OWNER}/${REPO_NAME}/issues/42"

# Or add when creating issue
gh issue create --title "Task" --label "phase-2" | \
    xargs -I {} gh project item-add 1 --owner ${GITHUB_OWNER} --url {}
```

## Map Issues to Status

After adding issues, update based on TASKLIST.md status:

```bash
