# Backlog (default for new issues) - [ ]
# Issues start here when created

# Ready - [ ] (defined in current phase)
gh project item-edit --id ITEM_ID --field-id STATUS_FIELD_ID --project-id PROJECT_ID --single-select-option-id "Ready"

# In Progress - [ ] üîÑ
